 crucial to the\nfundamental lemma in work of Mao and Rallis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Aug 2012 16:38:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2013 16:39:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-10"}
