ilarities,\nthis prior is able to borrow information from well-estimated main effects and\nlower-order interactions to assist in the estimation of higher-order terms for\nwhich data information is limited.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Aug 2012 18:21:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Apr 2014 11:47:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-15"}
