F), Average End-to-End Delay (AED), Average Throughput (AT),\nNormalized Routing Load (NRL) and Average Jitter and Accumulated Average\nProcessing Time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2012 15:58:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-10"}
